@ENDNODE

@NODE bugs "Known bugs"

 Known Bugs
 ----------

 Some JPEG datatypes don't return a perfect picture, if this happens on
 your system, try changing to a different JPEG/JFIF datatype.
 there are several different version available on aminet an CoverCD's.
 - Also happens for Multiview - on WB windows


 Send any reports to e-mail address.

@ENDNODE

